{"tid":1439794,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［香港人一條心］全部人入晒嚟！！遊行 死線 大作戰！！","createTime":"2019-08-10T08:27:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T09:20:18.000Z","uid":280717,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"62b21326c5aa1813331dfe1ffa66dd8af5874b2e","tid":1439794,"uid":280717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:27:44.000Z","msg":"首先想幫手推下呢個Post<br />\n[一人一票] 8月大型和平遊行 - 遊行/死線/升級日期<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1439215\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1439215</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n抗爭接近三個月<br />\n已經去到接近暑假尾段<br />\n大家亦深知假期一完<br />\n真係好多人都撐唔到落去<br />\n但係我想講<br />\n咁多位手足亦已經由示威者 暴徒 進化到抗爭者<br />\n<br />\n去到最後兩個星期<br />\n小弟有小小愚見：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">遊行 死線 大作戰</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1.最後大遊行</span></span><br />\n嚟近一定要有多次和理非大遊行<br />\n係大遊行 唔係小遊行<br />\n點解仲要和理非？仲要遊行？<br />\n答案好簡單<br />\n抗爭係為全香港市民 唔係為小數人<br />\n好多人話民意唔係最重要<br />\n但係冇咗民意唔會有咁成功<br />\n黃大仙市民係好出色嘅証明<br />\n<br />\n遊行好需要文宣組幫手<br />\n今次嘅目標<span style=\"color: red;\">唔只係普通和理非</span><br />\n而家<span style=\"color: red;\">包括勇武 家長 銀髮 所有香港人</span><br />\n同時要文宣吸引<span style=\"color: red;\">淺藍同中立</span><br />\n雖然佢哋到而家仲有咁嘅立場好pk<br />\n但只要唔係深藍就仲係香港人<br />\n要比佢係知道而家問題唔只係最近先出現<br />\n樓價上升(買唔到樓) 通脹乜乜乜(乜都好L貴)<br />\n都係長遠以來政府無能所致<br />\n唔想有害群之馬影響警隊都要出嚟(<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n同埋話比中立淺藍知<br />\n如果今次<span style=\"color: red;\">遊行成功贏到政府</span><br />\n暴徒就可以<span style=\"color: red;\">冇後續行為</span><br />\n一天都光晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之 你明啦<br />\n盡可能搞一次集合最多人嘅遊行<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">2.死線</span></span><br />\n要set好deadline！<br />\n無論係喺遊行前或者後<br />\n都要正正式式做個廣播<br />\n可以係民間記者會<br />\n可以係直接搵記者採訪<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有文有路中英宣讀</span><br />\n前幾次宣讀都好大迴響<br />\n比好多人知道大家係冷靜文明嘅<br />\n亦係爭取民意嘅方法之一<br />\n內容可以係遊行後<span style=\"color: red;\">政府嘅回應=市民嘅後續</span><br />\n總之講明和平遊行冇用<br />\n先至被迫使用其他抗爭手法<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">3.大作戰</span></span><br />\n呢個小弟唔識比意見<br />\n因為作戰經驗較小 睇live多D<br />\n所以唔敢亂講<br />\n但係睇咁多live都有啲得着<br />\n始終比較多角度<br />\n佢哋多用<span style=\"color: red;\">包圍同突擊</span>嘅方式<br />\n所以麻煩企最外圍嘅手足<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一定要有戰鬥同危險意識</span><br />\n點解我話最外圍而唔係最前線？<br />\n因為捉人嗰陣冇真正嘅前線<br />\n只有真係嘅外圍<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">最左最右最後都危險</span><br />\n所以如果夠人多嘅話<br />\n勇武應該係<span style=\"color: red;\">以圍牆陣線保住其他手足</span><br />\n真正勇武唔使太多<br />\n因為全部人同一陣線<br />\n你哋係最高攻嘅武士<br />\n其他係<span style=\"color: red;\">以量取勝嘅士兵</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">可以救人 可以助攻</span><br />\n<br />\n另外係最後一次大戰<br />\n個人認為希望唔好玩遊擊<br />\n而係集中力量<br />\n對準目的地(大家之後再傾？)<br />\nAll in ，搏一Po<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山，各自努力。<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n<br />\n香港是我家，全城守護它。</span></span>"},{"pid":"f49883fc1570a53f5723c884c79d546e7c386a55","tid":1439794,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:28:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"60971e085c183680ef52cf00719412d96c99ebb3","tid":1439794,"uid":280717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:28:27.000Z","msg":"推 last two week"},{"pid":"b1d47f7d1f2c87f221f0a5fd9b9b8faf9cbf957f","tid":1439794,"uid":280717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:29:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c6791e125683094852acb9c8560f7cae47bb34ac","tid":1439794,"uid":280717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:29:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"af965788f91c934db805927d1f17ec5e3779a385","tid":1439794,"uid":280717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:29:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1c410735e56f401649db78b4404319b43b7df4e3","tid":1439794,"uid":280717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:30:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1d7f62bdbada7ab235a4a81ffdbe9e534456508f","tid":1439794,"uid":280717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:30:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a64f2ebd725be49cda950ab24ea8e3771a095ddb","tid":1439794,"uid":76577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:30:39.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思阻阻你<br />\n<br />\n食人血饅頭既奶共地產商，就係我地黎緊既目標！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1435521\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1435521</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"60d26ebe83ace05076fad291f7e1897ba9317599","tid":1439794,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:30:59.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"7e18d84ce683804f399f7ef3268d51d44c4ce3cd","tid":1439794,"uid":280717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:31:58.000Z","msg":"同意嘅幫手推下"},{"pid":"6132ec4a04a21c564e1e3cbf670bb9208ada7953","tid":1439794,"uid":260325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:32:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa18a7c034ab078730597c3705e61999b36b0ad7","tid":1439794,"uid":280717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:32:49.000Z","msg":"唔該各位"},{"pid":"6353f82ae8c0e524bf9c00e4dbdd59e65af4367b","tid":1439794,"uid":280717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:33:05.000Z","msg":"可以嘅推下"},{"pid":"61e47b2f51b1adb51877cc188ccd06e58d1cc3f5","tid":1439794,"uid":280717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:33:38.000Z","msg":"和理非勇武全部入"},{"pid":"0c7878c880a63184f120cfaa65d77c8fb36762c7","tid":1439794,"uid":272942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:34:37.000Z","msg":"一定要"},{"pid":"91ca268dcfe1e3d3fdd06f58f1cc29feb03e5900","tid":1439794,"uid":280717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:35:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"64328a7b83a6d639452e3fd2605225f94fe145db","tid":1439794,"uid":280717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:35:23.000Z","msg":"share比身邊人<br />\n推下"},{"pid":"bce797e262c917733b231571521b1a0c6158f4fa","tid":1439794,"uid":280717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:37:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9370d88e3af878b058022a29124686dd009784c0","tid":1439794,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:37:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">推行動post呀<br />\n- 新增寶湖路線圖(By 八塊田巴打)<br />\n- 新增 612Reminder設防圖片<br />\n<br />\n 【置頂+廣傳】８.１０ 大 埔 逃 生 路 線 圖 （附 廣 場 名）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438647\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438647</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span>"},{"pid":"7b1a92fc40c876fa002da71ccd675ee05efe1f3f","tid":1439794,"uid":280717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:44:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"14dffdba6a75f1dbdf46b156dabad0c677685918","tid":1439794,"uid":280717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:44:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"eb94a374a3fe39dddce8feb5c57042c9aa85ed93","tid":1439794,"uid":280717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:44:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"855010262bb5b7256db17f499975528d9db095dc","tid":1439794,"uid":280717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:45:10.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"94be62c32b9671ee3de18a2ab1309076ce58e26d","tid":1439794,"uid":295639,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:45:28.000Z","msg":"大遊行認同<br />\n限期都認同<br />\n遊擊進攻都認同<br />\n但絕不死守<br />\n記者到了，直播開通之後，若然班狗預備進攻就要立刻棄守<br />\n一個都不能少"}]}